Package: projectr
Title: Data Analysis Prroject Tools
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Matthew",
           family = "Edwards",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mtedwards@protonmail.com")
Description: projectr provides tools to facilitate a data analysis project. 
  These tools include a function to structure the project directory, a function 
  to set up a data directory external to the project directory, a function to 
  get the absolute path to files in the data directory and a function to git 
  ignore files.
